      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FANTASTIC IRIS (6) has a strong record this track and trip with two wins and three placings from six starts. In the money last time at this track (30.14) in a Mix 2/3, finishing a 5.5 lengths third. Looks a key chance on best form. ZIPPING KENDRICK (3) scored two back with ease when racing on speed but drifted back and missed the frame latest finishing a 5.5 lengths 6th at Maitland (22.95). Likely to play a prominent role. NORDIC SHIRAZ (4) doesn't win out of turn. Finished second (30.52) at this track latest and might be close to finding winning form again. Form at the trip sound including six wins. Expected to feature. I'LL SEE (1) cannot be left out over a shorter trip.",
